cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper presents a teleoperation system for remote robots. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the system uses vision guidance for the teleoperation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the system uses a coarse-to-fine controller for guiding the robot. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the system deals with time-delay network conditions and control of the remote robot. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also relevant as the paper discusses the telepresence interface for the human operator.
